        "derivation": "$\\frac{x + 1}{2} = 2 \\Rightarrow x + 1 = 4 \\Rightarrow x = 3 \\\\ \\frac{y + 4}{2} = -3 \\Rightarrow y + 4 = -6 \\Rightarrow y = -10 \\\\ A = (3, -10)$"
